## UI components

- **PageHero:** `src/components/PageHero.jsx` — editorial heroes; spec in `docs/imagery-system.md`.
- **Select:** `src/components/Select.jsx` — use for all dropdowns; spec in `docs/ui-design.md`.
- **Footer:** `src/components/Footer.jsx` — global footer; do not duplicate per page.
- **PremiumGate:** `src/components/PremiumGate.jsx` — premium content gating.
- **Auth:** `AuthForm`, `OtpVerifyForm`, `RequireAuth`, `RequireRole` in `src/components/auth/`; session in `src/context/AuthContext.jsx`. Signup requires email OTP — see [`docs/auth-membership-admin.md`](docs/auth-membership-admin.md).

## Nav order (primary)

Today · My Baby · My Care · Essentials · Community

Progress, Sources, Premium → footer only.

